    "description": "<strong>FIVE FANTASTIC SLOPES</strong><br>Battle against your friends as you race down the mountain slopes in this multiplayer battle-racing brawler!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2260350/extras/21f4ace23402e21fe464846f3f2cf94a.poster.avif?t=1708806484\" width=512 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2260350/extras/21f4ace23402e21fe464846f3f2cf94a.webm?t=1708806484\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2260350/extras/21f4ace23402e21fe464846f3f2cf94a.mp4?t=1708806484\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>TONS OF FUN ABILITIES</strong><br>Shoot, fly, and zoom your way to the finish line.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2260350/extras/18ac56f61ae31dcf48fc58bae050553c.poster.avif?t=1708806484\" width=512 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2260350/extras/18ac56f61ae31dcf48fc58bae050553c.webm?t=1708806484\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2260350/extras/18ac56f61ae31dcf48fc58bae050553c.mp4?t=1708806484\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>FUN WITH FRIENDS AND FAMILIY</strong><br>Play Online, through LAN, or try to beat the computers solo.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2260350/extras/324b862550fa85ef229f0693c619c0d9.poster.avif?t=1708806484\" width=512 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2260350/extras/324b862550fa85ef229f0693c619c0d9.webm?t=1708806484\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2260350/extras/324b862550fa85ef229f0693c619c0d9.mp4?t=1708806484\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>HOW-TO MULTIPLAYER</strong><br>Hosting a public game allows anyone up to 4 players (total) to join you (password optional). Private matches require a Steam invite or a Steam-Friends request to Join. Alternatively, you may connect via LAN (Local-Area-Network) for quick and easy connection within your household (Offline).<br><br>To invite a friend to a private match, press [shift+tab] while in game, select the Friends tab, right click a friend and press Invite to Game. Note, accepting an invite while the game is not running will only launch the game. The game must be up and running while accepting an invite to join the match.<br><br><strong>CONTROLLER SUPPORT</strong><br>Should work with just about any controller. You may want to leave steam input for controllers disabled for best control mapping.<br><br><strong>LYLEK GAMES</strong><br>Solo developer creating games that bring back that ol' homey, classic feel. Primarily focused on family-friendly, small group multiplayer games.",
